Citations
Date:  23/6/1898
Source:  Hawera Star
Author:
Vol / Page:  2
Edition:
Quote:  The Timaru A & P Association have set up a committee to communicate with other associations and obtain information with a view of recommending that steps be taken for the prevention of "trotting" or false bids at auction sales of stock. The practice is said to be very rife in that district.
